@Stephan: the diagnostic log in fact shows you already have the latest CLI 3.1.1. The alloy version is behind though.

Could you try uninstalling them from the command line and then reinstall to see if it helps?

{code}
sudo npm uninstall -g titanium
sudo npm uninstall -g alloy
npm cache clean
sudo npm install -g titanium
sduo npm install -g alloy
{code}

Thanks.
